ride v2: Strategy A recomputation, addressFromPublicKey, @Verifier, anomaly auto-pause

- verifyAndMint v2: recomputes keccak256(181B preimage) on-chain, cross-validates vs ZK proof
- Recipient: 32-byte DCC Curve25519 public key via addressFromPublicKey()
- @Verifier blocks DataTransactions to prevent replay entry deletion
- Anomaly auto-pause at 2x hourly cap, checkpoint freshness check (7 days)
- Two-phase unpause: requestUnpause + executeUnpause with 100-block delay
- Enhanced audit trail: processed_at + minted_amount per message
- Ride equivalence test harness: 227 tests
- V-033/V-034 Ride-specific edge case vectors
- encoding.md v2.1: Ride constraints and complexity analysis
- RIDE_SECURITY_NOTE.md: verification boundary analysis

Tests: 227 RIDE + 236 TS + 12 Rust = 475 total, all passing
